type.name: org.gradle.tooling.model.DomainObjectSet
type.description:
A set of domain objects of type T.
param: The type of objects in this collection.

method.name: getAll
method.description:
Returns the elements of this set in the set's iteration order.

returns:The elements of this set in the set's iteration order.

method.name: getAt
method.description:
Returns the element at the given index according to the set's iteration order.
param:index The index of the element to get.

returns:The element at the given index according to the set's iteration order.
